name: Cladistic-15 'Krai Svarog' Filament
description:
The Cladistic-15 'Krai Svarog' Filament permits up to 15 ships to travel from Known Space to a system in Triglavian space controlled by the Svarog Clade.

Triglavian mastery of space-time conduit technology allows them relatively fine control over the generation and targeting of FTL conduits. The filament devices used by Triglavian forces aligned to Svarog Clade are connected to the artificial constellation of Krai Svarog. Even those unfamiliar with how to precisely target them will find the conduits they generate will transport them to Svarog-controlled space.
